<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.995896>
    dc:description "FIGURE 9. Geographical distribution of Cubacanthozomus and related genera." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/995896/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.995902>
    dc:description "FIGURES 14 ‒ 15. Cubacanthozomus rowlandi (male from Cueva de Máximo, Baracoa). Opisthosomal chaetotaxy: 14, sternites V ‒ VIII; 15, sternite IX + segments X – XII." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/995902/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.995904>
    dc:description "FIGURE 16. Cubacanthozomus rowlandi (male from Cueva de Máximo, Baracoa). Last abdominal segments and flagellum, lateral aspect, showing modified setae on segments XI and XII." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/995904/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.995890>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 ‒ 4. Cubacanthozomus rowlandi (male from Cueva de Máximo, Baracoa). 1, abdominal segments XI ‒ XII and flagellum, dorsolateral aspect. 2 ‒ 4, flagellum, in dorsal (2), ventral (3), and lateral (4) aspects. Scale: 1 = 0.22 mm; 2 ‒ 4 = 0.16 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/995890/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.995892>
    dc:description "FIGURES 5 ‒ 7. Cubacanthozomus rowlandi (female from Cueva de Máximo, Baracoa). 5 ‒ 6, flagellum in dorsal (5), and lateral (6) aspects. 7, spermathecae." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/995892/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.995898>
    dc:description "FIGURE 10. Cubacanthozomus rowlandi (female from Cueva de Máximo, Baracoa). Chelicera showing group 1 setae (G 1); s = serrula." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/995898/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.995900>
    dc:description "FIGURES 11 ‒ 13. Cubacanthozomus rowlandi (male from Cueva de Máximo, Baracoa). Pedipalp chaetotaxy: 11, trochanter and femur, ectal; 12, femur and patela, mesal; 13, patela and tibia, ventral." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/995900/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.995894>
    dc:description "FIGURES 8. Cubacanthozomus rowlandi (female from Cueva de Máximo, Baracoa). 8, genital atrium (G. A.) and posterior branch of the chitinized arch (C. A.)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/995894/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

